      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p5",
      "section_id": "s0",
      "section_path": [],
      "ordinal": 5,
      "text": "As NLdigital, the leading trade association of the digital industry in the Netherlands, we attach great value to strong consumer protection and a well-functioning digital internal market. For this reason, we wish to share our concerns about the necessity and proportionality of the upcoming Digital Fairness Act (DFA).",
      "char_len": 318,
      "chunk_word_count": 48,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9704797047970479,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8522012578616353
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9778597785977861,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p6",
      "section_id": "s1",
      "section_path": [
        "Our message: existing frameworks are sufficient"
      ],
      "ordinal": 6,
      "text": "Europe already has one of the most comprehensive consumer protection systems in the world. Instruments such as the Unfair Commercial Practices Directive (UCPD), the Consumer Rights Directive (CRD), the Price Indication Directive (PID), the Digital Services Act (DSA), the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), the ePrivacy Directive, the Digital Markets Act (DMA), and the AI- and Data Act provide robust protection.",
      "char_len": 421,
      "chunk_word_count": 61,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9390581717451524,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8574821852731591
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9542936288088644,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p7",
      "section_id": "s1",
      "section_path": [
        "Our message: existing frameworks are sufficient"
      ],
      "ordinal": 7,
      "text": "The challenges identified by the Commission – such as dark patterns, addictive design, harmful personalization, and misleading pricing practices – are challenges we recognize, and which must be addressed where necessary. However, these challenges are already covered sufficiently by existing, solid legislative frameworks. The problem lies in inconsistent and fragmented enforcement. New rules would be redundant and lead to more legal uncertainty. This would harm the competitive position and innovative capacity of Europe.",
      "char_len": 524,
      "chunk_word_count": 71,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9712389380530974,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8625954198473282
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.978429203539823,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p8",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Call for action"
      ],
      "ordinal": 8,
      "text": "We call on the European Commission to draw attention to the following three points in European decision-making:",
      "char_len": 111,
      "chunk_word_count": 17,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9789473684210527,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8558558558558559
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5105994152046784,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p9",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Call for action"
      ],
      "ordinal": 9,
      "text": "Strengthen enforcement: invest in more coordinated and harmonized application of existing rules.",
      "char_len": 96,
      "chunk_word_count": 12,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9764705882352941,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8854166666666666
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.43235294117647055,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p10",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Call for action"
      ],
      "ordinal": 10,
      "text": "Improve cooperation: prevent fragmentation through closer cooperation between authorities and Member States.",
      "char_len": 108,
      "chunk_word_count": 12,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.979381443298969,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8981481481481481
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.43453608247422676,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p11",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Call for action"
      ],
      "ordinal": 11,
      "text": "Stimulate simplification: ensure digital information provision by default and phase out outdated obligations.",
      "char_len": 109,
      "chunk_word_count": 13,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.979381443298969,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8899082568807339
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.44981386025200454,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p12",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Call for action"
      ],
      "ordinal": 12,
      "text": "If the Digital Fairness Act is presented as a legislative proposal, it needs to be targeted and proportionate, otherwise it threatens to be counterproductive and lead to unintended consequences. By choosing better enforcement of existing rules and simplification of the legal framework, we strengthen consumer protection, preserve the innovative capacity of our businesses, and contribute to a strong and competitive Europe.",
      "char_len": 424,
      "chunk_word_count": 61,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9807692307692307,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8584905660377359
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9855769230769231,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p13",
      "section_id": "s2",
      "section_path": [
        "Call for action"
      ],
      "ordinal": 13,
      "text": "In this letter, below, you will find a brief analysis of every topic.",
      "char_len": 69,
      "chunk_word_count": 13,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9473684210526315,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8260869565217391
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.42580409356725146,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
