    },
    {
      "para_id": "p36",
      "section_id": "s4",
      "section_path": [
        "Dark patterns"
      ],
      "ordinal": 36,
      "text": "New legislation on this point is unnecessary and may undermine legitimate design choices that improve user experience.",
      "char_len": 118,
      "chunk_word_count": 17,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9901960784313726,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.864406779661017
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.5190359477124183,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p37",
      "section_id": "s5",
      "section_path": [
        "Pricing practices"
      ],
      "ordinal": 37,
      "text": "Unfair pricing practices are already prohibited under the CRD, UCPD, and the Price Indication Directive (PID). Dynamic pricing comes in a wide range of forms applied varyingly in different industries or business models. Therefore, a broad restriction of the practice should be avoided as dynamic pricing can have significant benefits for consumers and businesses.",
      "char_len": 363,
      "chunk_word_count": 54,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9741935483870968,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8539944903581267
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9806451612903226,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p38",
      "section_id": "s5",
      "section_path": [
        "Pricing practices"
      ],
      "ordinal": 38,
      "text": "For example, it can lead to better and faster allocation of resources as it improves the matching of fluctuating demand and supply, lower prices for consumers, intensified competition between businesses, easier entry by new businesses by reducing the cost of setting and changing prices, and improved inventory management. What is needed is better enforcement – not new rules.",
      "char_len": 376,
      "chunk_word_count": 57,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9749216300940439,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.848404255319149
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.9811912225705329,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p39",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Addictive design"
      ],
      "ordinal": 39,
      "text": "A distinction must be made between risky practices and legitimate features that increase ease of use and engagement, such as recommendations or dynamic content. The DSA already provides specific protection for minors:",
      "char_len": 217,
      "chunk_word_count": 32,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9838709677419355,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8571428571428571
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.7434587813620073,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p40",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Addictive design"
      ],
      "ordinal": 40,
      "text": "Art. 25: prohibits design of an interface that \"deceives or manipulates\" users or \"materially distorts\" decisions.",
      "char_len": 114,
      "chunk_word_count": 16,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9090909090909091,
        "digit": 0.020202020202020204,
        "non_space": 0.868421052631579
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.4429292929292929,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p41",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Addictive design"
      ],
      "ordinal": 41,
      "text": "Art. 28: already ensures that online platforms take appropriate measures to protect minors.",
      "char_len": 91,
      "chunk_word_count": 13,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9367088607594937,
        "digit": 0.02531645569620253,
        "non_space": 0.8681318681318682
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.417809423347398,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p42",
      "section_id": "s6",
      "section_path": [
        "Addictive design"
      ],
      "ordinal": 42,
      "text": "Broad prohibitions would have disproportionate consequences for industries where \"addictive use\" is not an issue.",
      "char_len": 113,
      "chunk_word_count": 15,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9696969696969697,
        "digit": 0.0,
