      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p52",
      "section_id": "s7",
      "section_path": [
        "Personalization"
      ],
      "ordinal": 52,
      "text": "Additional rules under the DFA would lead to overlap, ambiguity, and loss of legal predictability.",
      "char_len": 98,
      "chunk_word_count": 15,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9642857142857143,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8571428571428571
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.46904761904761905,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p53",
      "section_id": "s8",
      "section_path": [
        "Horizontal proposals"
      ],
      "ordinal": 53,
      "text": "Concepts such as \"fairness by design,\" a redefinition of the \"average consumer,\" an expanded category of \"vulnerable consumers\" (for example, emotional stress) or reversing the burden of proof would lead to legal uncertainty and disproportionate burdens, especially for SME businesses:",
      "char_len": 285,
      "chunk_word_count": 40,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9471544715447154,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8631578947368421
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.8381436314363144,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "threshold+top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p54",
      "section_id": "s8",
      "section_path": [
        "Horizontal proposals"
      ],
      "ordinal": 54,
      "text": "GDPR art. 25: \"data protection by design and by default\" already embodies a fairness principle.",
      "char_len": 95,
      "chunk_word_count": 15,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9135802469135802,
        "digit": 0.024691358024691357,
        "non_space": 0.8526315789473684
      },
      "meaning": {
        "score": 0.43101851851851847,
        "flags": []
      },
      "selection": {
        "selected": true,
        "policy": "top_k"
      },
      "chunk_quality": "ok"
    },
    {
      "para_id": "p55",
      "section_id": "s8",
      "section_path": [
        "Horizontal proposals"
      ],
      "ordinal": 55,
      "text": "Vulnerable consumers are overall already covered in:",
      "char_len": 52,
      "chunk_word_count": 7,
      "ratios": {
        "alpha": 0.9782608695652174,
        "digit": 0.0,
        "non_space": 0.8846153846153846
      },
      "meaning": {
